'''Aadii companies... Gujranwala Electric Power Company''' (GEPCO) is an electric distribution company which supplies electricity to [[Gujranwala|Gujranwala Region]], [[Punjab (Pakistan)|Punjab]], [[Pakistan]]. The jurisdiction of the company includes Sialkot, Narowal, Gujranwala, Gujrat and Mandi Bahauddin Districts. Choudhary Muhammad Akram is current Chief Executive Officer (CEO) GEPCO. The main man-force of the company includes Line Staff, Clerecal Staff, Reading Staff and Officers / Managers. The company has more than 15000 employees with 300+ officers.

